quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  53,33,Abaffe olabye oyo akyuka (naava ku mazima)
  53,34,Era nawaayo katono bwamala ate nammira ddala
  53,35,"Abaffe (ekimukozesa ekyo) lwakuba nti alina okumanya ebyekusifu, olwo nno naaba nga abiraba"
  53,36,Oba tabuulirwanga ebyo ebiri mu bitabo bya Musa
  53,37,Ne Ibrahim oyo eyatuukiriza (bwe yalaganyisa Katonda)
  53,38,(Ebyo ebigamba nti) tewali mwoyo gulyetikka kibi kya mulala
  53,39,Era nti omunu tagenda kufuna okugyako ekyo kye yakolerera
  53,40,Era nti mazima okukola kwe kya ddaaki kulirabwa
  53,41,Oluvanyuma alikusasulwamu empeera esinga okuba enzijuvu
  53,42,Era nti mazima ewa Mukama omulabirizi wo yeeri enkomerero (ya buli kimu)
  53,43,Era nti mazima yye yaasesa era yaakaabya
  53,44,Era nti mazima yye yatta era yaawa obulamu
  53,45,Era nti mazima yatonda emitindo ebiri omusajja n'omukazi
  53,46,Abagya mu mazzi agazaala bwe gafulumizibwa (negateekebwa mu kifo ekituufu)
  53,47,Era nti mazima kuli ku ye yekka okusibusa okulala (okuzuukiza)
  53,48,Era nti mazima yye ya gaggawaza era naayavuwaza
  53,49,Era nti mazima yye ye Mukama omulabirizi we munyeenye eyitibwa Shiiraa (abakafiiri gye basinzanga)
  53,50,Era nti mazima yye yazikiriza abe kibiina kya A'adi abasooka
  53,51,Na be kibiina kya Thamud era nga teyalekawo (wadde omu)
  53,52,Na bantu ba Nuhu mu kusooka anti mazima bo be baali basinga okweyisa obubi n'okubula
  53,53,Era ye yae yazikiriza abantu ba be kitundu ekyavuunikibwa (Sodoma ne gomora)
  53,54,Olwo nno ne kikibuutikira ekya kibuutikira
  53,55,Kale olwo kiriwa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabiri wo kyobuusabuusa
  53,56,Ono (omubaka Muhammad) mutiisa ali mu luse lwa batiisa abaakulembera
  53,57,Enkomerero esembedde
  53,58,Tewali ayinza kugizzaayo bweriba ezze mpozzi Katonda
  53,59,Abaffe ebigambo bino bye mujereegerera
  53,60,Nemuba nga museka nemutakaaba
  53,61,Nga nammwe muzannya buzannyi
  53,62,Kale muvunname ku lwa Katonda era mumusinze (ekyo kye kisinga ebya mmwe bye mulimu)